high_descs: Turn around, and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife.
Turn left, walk past the sink, and turn right.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Turn around, walk to the counter, turn left, and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the knife in the fridge, and close the fridge.
Turn around, walk to the counter, turn right, and walk to the counter.
Pick up a potato slice.
Turn around, walk to the counter, turn left, and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the potato slice in the fridge, close the fridge, open the fridge, pick up the potato slice, and close the fridge.
Face the trashcan to the right.
Put the potato slice in the trashcan.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in the fridge, and a cold potato slice in the trashcan.

high_descs: Turn around and step forward to face the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn left to face the potato on the sink.
Cut the potato on the sink into slices.
Turn right and walk forward to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Turn left and step forward to face the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Turn right and walk forward to face the fridge.
Cool the potato slice in the fridge and remove it.
Step to the right to face the trash can.
Place the potato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To cool a potato slice and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink
Pick up the knife in the sink
Move a bit to the left
Slice the potato on the counter
Turn around, go forward ,turn left and go to the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Turn around, go forward, turn right and go to the counter
Pick up an potato slice from the counter
Turn around, go forward ,turn left and go to the fridge
Put the potato slice in the fridge, wait, pick up the potato slice from the fridge
Move a bit to the right
Put the potato slice in the bin
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, cool a slice, an throw it into the bin
